response.original_title: Oakland Oaks vs. San Francisco Seals baseball opening. 1918-04-02
response.overview: Footage from the festivities for the opening day of the Oakland Oaks baseball season, versus the San Francisco Seals. The film features vaudeville dancer Doraldina, who is dressed in a baseball uniform and appears with the team in a parade and on the field, eventually throwing the ceremonial first pitch.
response.title: Oakland Oaks vs. San Francisco Seals baseball opening. 1918-04-02
